{"tid":2376280,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"PLTR YES","createTime":"2021-01-22T16:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T04:39:57.000Z","uid":318236,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"0a59cb0ea446135d59305f61ae0c54fbfdb88463","tid":2376280,"uid":318236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:08:00.000Z","msg":"Palantir Technologies Inc.(<a href=\"http://PLTR.US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FPLTR.US&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=e5b10ac8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">PLTR.US</a>)成立於2003年，總部位於美國科羅拉多州丹佛，為美國情報界建立及部署軟體平台，藉以輔助反制恐怖主義調查及和行動。公司提供的Palantir Gotham為一個軟體平台，供政府防衛及情報部門使用，允許使用者可識別隱藏在資料集深處的模型，涵蓋訊號情報來源至機密情報員的報告，並簡化分析員及操作使用者間的换手，幫助操作者計劃及執行平台內已認定威脅的真實反應。公司亦提供Palantir Foundry，透過其數據建立中央操作系統藉以改變組織營運方式的平台；並允許個人使用者在一個位置整合及分析其所需的數據。<br />\n<a href=\"https://money.moneydj.com/us/basic/basic0001/PLTR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.moneydj.com%2Fus%2Fbasic%2Fbasic0001%2FPLTR&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5DsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=aa67cc50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://money.moneydj.com/us/basic/basic0001/PLTR</a>"},{"pid":"6380d7598f82c65550d1797531aaf0510b33d274","tid":2376280,"uid":318236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7954c605dfd2022805a96fbe624bbdb160e6f67b","tid":2376280,"uid":318236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:08:48.000Z","msg":"最後上車機會"},{"pid":"22b9509cef2afd76e29295c4bd4f1ee3f0edd313","tid":2376280,"uid":180772,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"靜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ad07a07ab114dc7f42c90ca34a0df77d13a458","tid":2376280,"uid":318236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2